message.entry: ''DataVariables'' and ''ReplaceValues'' parameters are only supported for table inputs.
''DataVariables'' function handle must return a logical scalar.
First argument must be numeric, logical, datetime, duration, calendarDuration, categorical, char, cellstr, string, table, or timetable.
Parameter name must be either ''DataVariables'' or ''ReplaceValues''.
Incorrect number of input arguments. Parameter names and values must occur in pairs.
First argument must be numeric, logical, duration, string, categorical, char, or table.
